Program -2: Create  a  Pyramid  program  in Java1.0
----------------------------------------------------

longestpal.jav
--------------

<JAVA>
@Package
<%




public class longestpal
{
public void  JAVA-Main( )  throws  <EXE>
{
for(int i=5; i>0 ;i--){
                       
                        for(int j=0; j < i; j++){
                                JAVA.out.writeln(""+j+1);
                               
                                
                        }
                       JAVA.out.writeln(""+ " ");
                        
                }
 
 
}
}


%>

</JAVA>

Note:
------

compile the  program  by  using  longestpal.jav

